stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_pop: pop x from stack
    q_pop --> q_check_zero: read x
    q_check_zero --> q_return_256: x == 0
    q_check_zero --> q_compute: x != 0
    q_compute --> q_push: r = 256 - len(bin(x))
    q_return_256 --> q_push: r = 256
    q_push --> [*]: push r to stack
